parameters: If you got some wood, we can craft some sticks.
If you're wondering, the mine has a magical
force field where you can actually re-mine
the materials every hour and a half.
The perfect beloved location for merchants.
Ah, a newcomer to the forest! I’m Eldon, the Forest Guide.
Every lumberjack begins with their first chop. Take this
old axe of mine—it’s not much, but it’ll do the job.
Bring me back 30 pieces of wood, and I’ll see that you’re
properly equipped for the challenges ahead.

parameters.name: Lumberjack's First Quest
parameters.description: Gather 30 pieces of wood and return to Eldon.
